\end{align*}Then $x_1 + x_2 = 1,$ $y_1 + y_2 = 0,$ and $z_1 + z_2 = 1.$  Squaring these equations, we get
\begin{align*}
x_1^2 + 2x_1 x_2 + x_2^2 &= 1, \\
